{"tid":698122,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓價走勢】戴德梁行：全年樓價料升夠20%","createTime":"2018-06-11T12:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T04:10:57.000Z","uid":68476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"879d14533c14bd7406969566951162640d4eda3f","tid":698122,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"【樓價走勢】戴德梁行：全年樓價料升夠20%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180611/large/1528707472_f743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180611%2Flarge%2F1528707472_f743.jpg&h=ee1b6042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴德梁行陶汝鴻(右)認為，上半年樓價升勢已超出預期<br />\n<br />\n戴德梁行大中華區副總裁陶汝鴻表示，根據土地註冊處資料及戴德梁行數據，住宅物業上半年至今已升11.5%，而今年初預期上半年升幅10%，現在已超出預期。成交價有成交量支持，今年首季一手及二手成交量按年增約23%，次季按年跌2%。<br />\n<br />\n其中沙田第一城今年上半年升14.3%，按年升19.3%，若比較2016年4月低位，升68.4%。鰂魚涌太古城今年上半年升14.8%，按年升19.2%，比較2016年4月升59.6%。<br />\n<br />\n陶汝鴻表示，今年下半年肯定加息，但步伐及速度不會明顯，對樓市影響唔會話無，有心理影響，但實際影響不大。加息代表經濟向好抵銷負面影響。至於一手空置稅，但只是新盤市場，而且數量不多，僅數千宗，在以萬計成交量而言，影響不大。反而關注發展商會否將稅款轉嫁消費者。<br />\n<br />\n不過下半年不明朗因素主要是加息及一手空置稅，從而令<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">下半年樓價升幅放緩，升幅較上半年慢，料升5至8%，全年累計升幅20%。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f848b30b7ac4f904629e6aaa0f3cde2bb92afb9","tid":698122,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"爆未牙？"},{"pid":"fc7daebd48b0888ecec76d19624599653654b51c","tid":698122,"uid":40207,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02dea90dc55f9cd852719a91db578a8cd2a7d9aa","tid":698122,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"無30%唔收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ec6826f204528f2734f775a97a186c8f480a87","tid":698122,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f848b30b7ac4f904629e6aaa0f3cde2bb92afb9","tid":698122,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"爆未牙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"爆升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eca558084cb9f9d05363890fc33e7b11e226160","tid":698122,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T04:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}